entry.title: davimang/REACH
entry.summary:
A web application used to improve patients' access to clinical trials and practitioners' access to potential participants.

REACH

Developer Names: David Moroniti, Deep Raj, Alan Scott, Anika Peer, Aamina Hussain

Date of project start: 11/18/2023

This project is a full-stack web application used to improve patients' access to clinical trials and practitioners' access to potential participants.

The folders and files for this project are as follows:

docs - Documentation for the project refs - Reference material used for the project, including papers src - Source code test - Test cases etc.
